1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 6=

3
00:00:56,679 --> 00:00:58,719
Why won't you just kill me?

4
00:01:03,039 --> 00:01:05,719
Why would I let you die so easily?

5
00:01:07,319 --> 00:01:09,359
Didn't you enjoy having male consorts?

6
00:01:10,959 --> 00:01:13,319
You'll learn what it means to crawl

7
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:16,359
and beg for your life.

8
00:01:19,359 --> 00:01:21,120
When I ascend the throne,

9
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:24,959
you,
the once most honored person in Xiling,

10
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:28,079
will serve as a court singer

11
00:01:28,719 --> 00:01:30,920
just to amuse me.

12
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,120
You wretch!

13
00:01:37,959 --> 00:01:38,959
Your Highness.

14
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:41,640
Your Majesty.

15
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:43,920
I failed you.

16
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:47,519
I couldn't rescue you.

17
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,359
Miss,

18
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:06,040
how come you're out cold here alone?

19
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,319
Let me

20
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:11,759
check your wounds.

21
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:12,639
Come on.

22
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,520
Come on.

23
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:20,240
Run!

24
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,560
Miss? Miss?

25
00:02:30,639 --> 00:02:31,840
I owe you nothing this time.

26
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:34,599
Instead, you owe me a favor.

27
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,400
(Mu Ruyi,)

28
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,919
(pull yourself together.)

29
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,719
(Instead of a direct confrontation,)

30
00:02:47,719 --> 00:02:50,840
(why not turn his own schemes
back on him?)

31
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,280
Your Majesty.

32
00:03:18,919 --> 00:03:20,439
These are freshly tributed tangerines.

33
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:21,719
Try one.

34
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:24,159
These tangerines look really sweet,

35
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:25,360
but I think

36
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:28,639
if someone can kneel

37
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,400
and feed me,

38
00:03:32,639 --> 00:03:34,360
I'll enjoy them more.

39
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:48,680
I've changed my mind.

40
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:51,400
I want you

41
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,560
to feed me with your mouth.

42
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,680
How come you changed your demeanor?

43
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:24,360
Or should I say

44
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:28,240
that your true nature is dissolute?

45
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,199
I've thought it over.

46
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:32,839
Instead of tormenting myself over

47
00:04:33,079 --> 00:04:34,439
what cannot be changed,

48
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,399
I would do better to accept the present
as it is

49
00:04:37,759 --> 00:04:38,920
and plan for the long term.

50
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,279
You are still my husband.

51
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:46,399
Do you truly mean that?

52
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,920
Yes, I do.

53
00:05:23,959 --> 00:05:25,199
I made this dinner myself.

54
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,199
I hope you enjoy it.

55
00:05:54,199 --> 00:05:55,240
Will this do?

56
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,839
I have no intention of harming you.

57
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,600
Go ahead and enjoy.

58
00:06:03,199 --> 00:06:05,079
This is the life I've always wanted.

59
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,839
You and I, an ordinary couple.

60
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,439
We share meals every day

61
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,199
and a happy life forever.

62
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:29,160
Mu Ruyi,

63
00:06:32,319 --> 00:06:33,759
if I didn't know you well,

64
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:37,279
I might have been fooled by your words.

65
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:42,360
But don't forget the debt between us.

66
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,199
A strategic delay

67
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:47,800
can't fool me.

68
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:50,120
You'd better pray

69
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:52,720
that I don't lose interest in you
too soon.

70
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,040
I accept it.

71
00:07:05,079 --> 00:07:05,959
Stupid woman!

72
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:08,000
Your life belongs to me!

73
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:10,600
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

74
00:07:15,079 --> 00:07:15,879
It seems

75
00:07:16,639 --> 00:07:17,839
you care about me

76
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,519
more than I expected.

77
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,240
You flatter yourself.

78
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:23,480
You are just one of my toys.

79
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,160
If you're broken,

80
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,199
you'll be worthless.

81
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,120
Stop denying it.

82
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,040
You do care about me.

83
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:04,240
You've schemed for years,

84
00:08:04,639 --> 00:08:06,120
and all your plots and designs

85
00:08:06,759 --> 00:08:07,920
were just to have me.

86
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,160
Even if I'm just a toy,

87
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:13,399
I'm still the one
Your Majesty cannot forget.

88
00:08:14,319 --> 00:08:15,439
You dare not kill me,

89
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:17,040
because if you do,

90
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:20,560
your life will drift
like a kite cut loose.

91
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,360
Everything will be meaningless.

92
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,519
Trying to irritate me?

93
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,639
You're far from it.

94
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:13,279
Show me your petty schemes.

95
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:14,759
Ling Xiao,

96
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:17,399
do you remember this melody?

97
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,679
The day we first met,

98
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,039
all was well.

99
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,120
What do you mean?

100
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:27,600
I cut ties with my mother just for you.

101
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,519
So you should know

102
00:10:30,879 --> 00:10:32,559
my feelings for you are real.

103
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:37,279
I've questioned myself many nights,

104
00:10:37,879 --> 00:10:39,360
and even though you hurt me deeply,

105
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,960
my heart still belongs to you.

106
00:11:20,879 --> 00:11:21,600
Just as I thought,

107
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:24,200
it was all your scheme.

108
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,519
My scheme?

109
00:11:26,279 --> 00:11:27,679
Doesn't it feel familiar?

110
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,039
From the very beginning,

111
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:31,360
this is what you did to me.

112
00:11:31,879 --> 00:11:34,159
I just learned from you

113
00:11:34,919 --> 00:11:36,320
and turned your schemes against you.

114
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:38,879
Our encounter, from the beginning,

115
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:41,080
was a complete conspiracy.

116
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,840
A broken mirror cannot be made whole.

117
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,679
Spilled water cannot be gathered back.

118
00:11:46,879 --> 00:11:48,240
For all our lives and beyond,

119
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,679
we can only ever be enemies.

120
00:11:50,679 --> 00:11:51,639
I hate you.

121
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:54,120
You deserve to die a thousand times.

122
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:02,279
If you behave as my toy,

123
00:12:03,519 --> 00:12:05,320
I can guarantee you a life of comfort.

124
00:12:06,759 --> 00:12:08,360
But you've got some nerve

125
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:09,960
to insist on opposing me.

126
00:12:11,879 --> 00:12:15,200
Don't blame me for being merciless.

127
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,080
Merciless?

128
00:12:17,559 --> 00:12:20,039
Speak of mercy, you wretch?

129
00:12:20,639 --> 00:12:21,480
In this world,

130
00:12:21,679 --> 00:12:23,240
anyone who earns your affection

131
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:25,480
would be doomed to hell

132
00:12:25,679 --> 00:12:27,440
and could never rest in peace!

133
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,279
What are you doing?

134
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:40,320
I will live for myself.

135
00:12:42,639 --> 00:12:43,399
Mu Ruyi!
